    Usage in any .sls file:
      {% from 'host_config.jinja' import host %}
      {% if host.is_laptop %}
        ...laptop-specific states...
      {% endif %}

    To add a new host, create a new entry in the `hosts` dict.
    Any key not specified inherits from `defaults`.
#}

